## Quick Start

```bash
# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Run with web UI (opens at http://localhost:8089)
locust -f locustfile.py --host={{baseUrl}}

# Run headless (CLI mode)
locust -f locustfile.py --host={{baseUrl}} --headless -u 50 -r 10 --run-time 5m

# Run with HTML report
locust -f locustfile.py --host={{baseUrl}} --headless -u 50 -r 10 --run-time 5m --html=reports/report.html
```

